{"id":31330,"date":"2024-01-29T01:29:00","date_gmt":"2022-01-28T19:59:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=31330"},"modified":"2022-11-30T14:41:35","modified_gmt":"2022-11-30T09:11:35","slug":"modern-kitchen-island","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-island\/","title":{"rendered":"Add Space, Style And Storage With These Modern Kitchen Island Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Modern kitchen island ideas that will add storage and space to your kitchen<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kitchen islands are no longer just additional elements in kitchens. They are in trend and have even become the primary focal point of kitchen design aesthetics. Are you wondering what\u2019s the hype about? Well, the hype is because a modern kitchen island is not limited to just being an aesthetically pleasing interior element. A modern kitchen island is also an ideal way to multiply storage and cooking preparation areas. Gone are the days when kitchen islands were only for the lavish homes with spacious kitchen spaces. Today, kitchen islands come in various sizes, designs and attributes. Thus, they are the perfect element for interior personalisation.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>At Design Cafe, we bring a wide collection of modern kitchen island ideas to suit everyone and anyone. We have every type of modern kitchen island, whether you have a simple straight kitchen or a large U-shaped kitchen.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Kitchen Island Cum Breakfast Counter With Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern kitchen island has a multifunctional element and is ideal for small kitchen areas. Besides adding a separate preparation counter, the kitchen island also serves as a small breakfast space. The wooden top kitchen island also has a natural appeal that you will love if you have an industrial theme kitchen like this one. The counter height of the modern kitchen island is ergonomic. Hence it can also be a great place to work from home! Additionally, the kitchen island also has an open shelf cabinet beneath that serves as a bookshelf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen island cum breakfast counter with bookshelf\" data-id=\"31331\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31331\" class=\"wp-image-31331\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013255\/a-modern-kitchen-island-cum-breakfast-counter-with-bookshelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A wooden top modern kitchen island with a bookshelf<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trendy Modern Kitchen Island Designs With Cooking Counter<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern kitchen island design is the best option if you want to have a separate cooking counter. The kitchen island comes with an inbuilt hob, giving it a seamless appeal. The modern kitchen island also has enough space to keep frequently used utensils within reach when cooking. If that\u2019s not all, this modern kitchen island design also has enough space to serve as a breakfast counter. The front area of the kitchen island provides an ample amount of leg space, ideal for two people to sit and enjoy quick meals.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter.jpg\" alt=\"Trendy modern kitchen island designs with cooking counter\" data-id=\"31332\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31332\" class=\"wp-image-31332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013437\/trendy-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-cooking-counter-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A laminate top kitchen island with an inbuilt hob<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Extended Modern Kitchen Island Ideas With Storage Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern kitchen island design is for those who have a wide and spacious kitchen area. Matching with the rest of the kitchen\u2019s look, the kitchen island has a marble top with wooden cabinets beneath. The marble top design adds an exquisite royal look that is accentuated by the dark wooden cabinets beneath. The extended kitchen island has an inbuilt sink counter, making it the perfect place to rinse veggies and utensils. The extended countertop is ideal for at least four family members to sit together and eat. The modern kitchen island also multiplies the kitchen\u2019s storage with its extra cabinets. The extended countertop is perfect for houses with more than one chef.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets.jpg\" alt=\"Extended modern kitchen island ideas with storage cabinets\" data-id=\"31333\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31333\" class=\"wp-image-31333\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013632\/extended-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-with-storage-cabinets-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">An extended kitchen island with storage cabinets<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Design your modular kitchen that are smart like you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/27152054\/design-modular-kitchens-that-are-smart-like-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Broad Modern Kitchen Island Designs For Work From Home Needs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you been looking for an ergonomic counter height table to work from home? This is it! This modern kitchen island design is perfect as a breakfast cum work from the home counter. The tall height of the counter is ideal for sitting upright while working. The modern kitchen island also has a broad countertop area for comfortable cooking preparation. The kitchen island features a white marble top and a black laminate finish for the lower cabinet design, giving it a classic appeal. You can team it up with modern bar stools or raised dining chairs and use it as a bar counter during house parties.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs.jpg\" alt=\"Broad modern kitchen island designs for work from home needs\" data-id=\"31334\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31334\" class=\"wp-image-31334\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013805\/broad-modern-kitchen-island-designs-for-work-from-home-needs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A modern kitchen island with a broad countertop<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Granite Cum Wooden Kitchen Island With An Attached Breakfast Counter<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This kitchen island works as an additional cooking preparation area as well as a breakfast counter. The preparation area has a black granite top that borrows the look from the rest of the kitchen countertop. The breakfast counter has a raised wooden platform ideal for two people. This modern kitchen island design is ideal for a U-shaped kitchen. It can be placed right at the centre of the kitchen, making it the focal point of the kitchen\u2019s interiors. This modern kitchen island also has cabinets beneath that will multiply the storage option.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter.jpg\" alt=\"A granite cum wooden modern kitchen island designs with an attached breakfast counter\" data-id=\"31335\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31335\" class=\"wp-image-31335\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31013954\/a-granite-cum-wooden-modern-kitchen-island-designs-with-an-attached-breakfast-counter-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>A Sleek Modern Kitchen Island For An Uber Cool Kitchen Design<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern kitchen island design is ideal for sleek and minimalistic kitchen interiors. The flawless white laminate finish of the kitchen island adds a pristine appeal to the space. The kitchen island is excellent for cooking preparation or dining together while cooking. It has a broad and wide countertop area and can easily accommodate four to five family members at the breakfast counter. Team it up with armless, tall chairs to blend with the urban look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"A sleek modern kitchen island ideas for an uber cool kitchen design\" data-id=\"31336\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31336\" class=\"wp-image-31336\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31014135\/a-sleek-modern-kitchen-island-ideas-for-an-uber-cool-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern kitchen islands not only look great but are multifunctional too. They are ideal for additional storage and multiplying the kitchen counter area. In small kitchens, they can be a great way to add more storage. And in big kitchens, these modern kitchen island designs can become an aesthetic twist to break the monotony. Thus, a modern kitchen island is great for any kitchen. In case you need a design partner to build a personalised kitchen, reach out to us! So, go ahead and pick your favourite modern kitchen island ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking for Modular Kitchen Interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/05143011\/looking-for-modular-kitchen.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\